General.Name: Focus Minerals Limited
General.Description: Focus Minerals Limited engages in the exploration and development of gold in Western Australia. The company holds a 100% interest in the Coolgardie gold project located on the western side of the Archaean Norseman-Wiluna Greenstone belt within the Coolgardie Domain; and the Laverton gold project located in the Yilgarn Craton of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 1978 and is headquartered in East Perth, Australia. Focus Minerals Limited operates as a subsidiary of Shandong Gold International Mining Corporation Limited.
